{
  "page": "The Merchant's Melancholy Daughter",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>The Merchant's Melancholy Daughter</b></i> is a play performed by <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummers</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Scenes\">Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Merchant%27s_Melancholy_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In one popular scene a fat merchant defecates on the head of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord_of_Braavos\" title=\"Sealord of Braavos\">Sealord of Braavos</a> as his gold-and-purple barge passes underneath.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Izembaro\" title=\"Izembaro\">Izembaro</a> loves to give the Sealord's speech from the play, part of which goes, \"here the last Titan yet stands, astride the stony shoulders of his brothers.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Merchant%27s_Melancholy_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Merchant%27s_Melancholy_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>On her way to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_(playhouse)\" title=\"Gate (playhouse)\">Gate</a> for the performance of <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Bloody_Hand\" title=\"The Bloody Hand\">The Bloody Hand</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Mercy</a> recalls <i>The Merchant's Melancholy Daughter</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Merchant%27s_Melancholy_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Only in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> could something like that happen, it was said, and only in Braavos would <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord_of_Braavos\" title=\"Sealord of Braavos\">Sealord</a> and sailor alike howl with laughter to see it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-winds_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Merchant%27s_Melancholy_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-winds-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-winds_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, Mercy</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404064830\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 129/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 613/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2365/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 724/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 940/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.784      1 -total\n 30.29%    2.055      1 Template:Warning/twow\n 24.57%    1.667      1 Template:References\n 22.92%    1.555      1 Template:Warning\n 16.43%    1.115      1 Template:Quote\n 15.64%    1.061      1 Template:Mbox\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16937-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404064830 and revision id 261013\n -->\n",
